<HTML>
<HEAD>
    <TITLE>Your Booking</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<CENTER>
</BR>
Dear <B>$!name,</B>
</BR>
Thank you for booking your cab at PoolCabs. Please find the details of you booking(s) below.
</BR>
<table border="1" cellpadding="3">
    <tbody>
    <tr>
        <th>From</th>
        <th>To</th>        
        <th>Time</th>
        <th>Distance(KM)</th>

    </tr>
        #foreach( $!booking in $!bookingList )
        <tr>
            <td>$!booking.pickupStreetAddress</td>
            <td>$!booking.dropStreetAddress</td>            
            <td>$!booking.pickupTime</td>
            <td>$!booking.distanceInKM</td>
        </tr>
        #end
    </tbody>
</table>
This is an automated email message generated by PoolCabs. Please do not reply.
</BR>
Best Regards,
PoolCabs
</CENTER>
</BODY>
</HTML>